<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
    <link href="Style.css" type="text/css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Roboto&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <script src="Aplication.js"></script>
    <title>Peter</title>
</head>

<body>
    <section id="body-about">
        <header>
            <nav>
                <div class="logo"><a href="/"><img src="Design/logo5-mini.png" alt="logo"></a></div>
                <ul class="nav-links">
                    <li><a href="/about">About</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/login">Sign in</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/register">Register</a></li>
                </ul>
                <div class="burger">
                    <div class="line1"></div>
                    <div class="line2"></div>
                    <div class="line3"></div>
                </div>
            </nav>
        </header>

        <section class="about-rectangle">
            <p>About</p>
            <img id="about-logo" src="Design/logo5-mini.png" alt="logo">
        </section>

    </section>

    <section id="body-about-content">

        <div class = "about-container">
            <div class = "row">
                <div class = "column-66" >
                    <img id="fmi" src="Design/fmi.png" alt="fmi">
                </div>
                <article class = "column-33" id="who-i-am">
                    <p>Who I am?</p>
                    <p>I am a 20 years old Student in love with animals and Computer Science.</p>
                </article>

            </div>
        </div>

        <div class = "about-container">
            <div class = "row">
                <article class = "column-66" id="how-was-it-born">
                    <p>How was it born?</p>
                    <p>My brother’s Shih Tzu was having tough times finding a suitable mate, so I came with the idea of
                    creating a platform where people’s pets could interact with each other the way humans do on dating
                    sites.</p> 
                </article>
                <div class = "column-33" >
                    <img id="tzuca" src="Design/about2.jpeg" alt="tzuca">
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class = "about-container">
            <div class = "row">
                <div class = "column-66" >

                    <div class = "image-grid">

                        <div class = "image-item">
                            <button onclick = "openCaption()"><img src="Design/profile.png" alt = "profile" ></button>
                        </div>
                        <div class = "image-item">
                            <button onclick = "openCaption()"><img src="Design/explore.png" alt = "explore"></button>
                        </div>
                        <div class = "image-item">
                            <button onclick = "openCaption()"><img src="Design/chat.png" alt = "chat"></button>
                        </div>
                        <div class = "image-item">
                            <button onclick = "openCaption()"><img src="Design/love.png" alt = "love" id = "love"></button>
                        </div>

                    </div>

                </div>
                <article class = "column-33" id="how-does-it-work">
                    <p>How does it work?</p>
                    <ol id = "steps">
                        <li>Make a <span style="color:rgb(27,6,94);font-weight:bold">profile</span></li>
                        <li><span style="color:rgb(27,6,94);font-weight:bold">Explore</span> animals</li>
                        <li>Start <span style="color:rgb(27,6,94);font-weight:bold">conversations</span></li>
                        <li>Let your pet <span style="color:rgb(27,6,94);font-weight:bold">fall in love</span></li>
                    </ol>
                </article>

            </div>
        </div>

        <div class = "about-container">
            <div class = "row">
                <article class = "column-66" id="statistics">
                    <p>Statistics</p>
                    <p>Because the website is still being under construction, there aren't any profiles available.</p> 
                    <button type = "button" onclick = "loadText()" id = "ajax">Add</button>
                </article>
                <div class = "column-33" >
                    <table id = "stat">
                        <tr>
                            <th>Type</th>
                            <th>Profiles</th>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>Dogs</td>
                            <td>0</td>
                        </tr>
                            <td>Cats</td>
                            <td>0</td>
                        </tr>
                            <td>Birds</td>
                            <td>0</td>
                        </tr>
                    </table>

            
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>


    </section>

</body>

</html>